Package: play-launch
Architecture: any
Depends: ros-humble-desktop
Recommends: nvidia-utils
Description: ROS 2 launch inspection tool with resource monitoring
 Records and replays ROS 2 launch file executions for performance analysis.
 Features per-node resource monitoring (CPU, memory, I/O, network, GPU),
 interactive visualizations, and component container support.
